name: Wrap style pleated skirt dress
description: Formal fabric with a smooth surface, wrap-style dress. The waist size can be adjusted with the strap inserted into the waist of the right layer to create a dress fit, skirt pleated detail from the left body waist cut, long sleeves with a slim silhouette, and a pleated line at the back. Emphasis on lines with darts.

name: V-neck raglan short sleeve top
description: Soft and drapery white fabric, V-neck neatly finished with inner hem, raglan sleeves, a silhouette with side seams gathered toward the center of the front, double layer point at the front cut, and short length at the center of the front.

name: Linen short sleeve top
description: Linen fabric with a natural mood, basic round neck shape and 1/4" spaced inbinding for a neat finish, back neck keyhole opening, and a straight silhouette for plenty of room.

name: Cropped Asymmetric Frilled Top
description: Fitted long-sleeve top with a cropped asymmetric cut, frilled edges and a ribbed finish.

name: Round crop top
description: Soft cotton fabric, cropped length, basic round neck shape, half-length short sleeves, and finished with a fabric neckband.

name: V-neck shoulder detail top
description: Light fabric with a twill texture, two shoulder slits, chin details, V-neck shaped inner hem, volume created by pleats in the center of the sleeves, a clean scooty finish that holds the pleats at the end of the sleeves, and a sense of leisure with the pleat details in the center of the back.

name: Cowl neck side shirring top
description: Stretchy and comfortable fabric, drapery cowl neck, shirring details on both lower side seams, relatively short length and fitted silhouette.

name: Linen V-neck basic top
description: Courtyard linen fabric, V-neck shape with neat 1/4" gap inbinding finish, features a front center incision, and a straight box silhouette.

name: Boxy-Fit Curved-Hem T-Shirt
description: A boxy-fit T-shirt with a curved hem, short sleeves, and a round neckline.

name: Camisole tank top
description: Thick cotton fabric, camisole-style tank top, length adjustable with shoulder straps, features a princess line and chest slit, and a fitted line that highlights the silhouette.

name: V-neck lip trim detail setup
description: Combination of soft cotton fabric and ribbed fabric, neckband finished with ribs, ribbed trim that highlights the shoulder and arm lines, high ribbed cuffs, cropped length with differences in front and back length, waist elastic band pants, front Side seam crossed over, pocket located on the side seam line.

name: Sleeveless crop top
description: Lightweight fabric with crinkled texture, wide shoulder width with shoulder pad inserts, back keyhole button opening, 1/4" binding at center back, 1/4" binding strap ribbon tie at hem.

name: U-Neck Satin Sleeveless Top
description: Satin fabric with a soft touch and luster, neat inner hem finish with U-neck shape, and shirttail finish at the bottom.

name: Asymmetric V-neck blouse
description: Fabric with a sense of surface, V-neck shape and drapery asymmetrical layer at the center front slit, left side seam slit, 3/4 sleeves, pleated details on both sides based on the cuff opening.

name: High-neck halter sleeveless top
description: Dry textured cotton fabric, high neck halter style, shirring detail on the neck cut line, back neck keyhole and pearl button opening, armhole edge 1/4" inbinding finish, cropped length.

name: Basic t-shirt
description: Soft cotton fabric, basic round neck shape, short sleeves, and a clean finish.

name: Cigarette pants
description: Stretchy slacks fabric, cigarette silhouette with a fitted straight line and tapered hem, front button and zipper opening, pockets on both sides of the front and a central crease line, and a neat finish with darts on the back.

name: Tuck wide pants
description: Made of low-wrinkle cotton fabric with a surface feel, wide silhouette pants, tuck details on both sides of the center of the front, front buttons and zippers, side pockets on both front sides.

name: Bootcut ponte pants
description: Stretchy and thick ponte fabric, bootcut pants with a straight silhouette with a slightly wider hem, diagonal line pockets on both sides of the front, a yoke on the back, and welt pockets on both sides.

name: Elastic band pants
description: Light fabric with crinkled texture, waist belt loops, chin detail on the front belt loop line, front button and zipper opening, side pockets on both sides of the front, elastic inserts in the back waistband, and pentagonal patch pockets on both sides of the back.

name: Crinkled jogger pants
description: Light fabric with crinkled texture, chin detail on the waist belt loop line, side pockets between the chin cut and side cut, elastic bands at the waist and hem, and pentagonal patch pockets.

name: Raw edge chino pants
description: Chino cotton fabric, relatively thick waistband, two buttons and zipper opening, belt loops, streamlined side pockets on both sides and right key pocket, straight and fitted silhouette, raw edge treatment at the bottom.

name: Belted cigarette pants
description: Stretchy slack fabric with a soft touch, waist belt connected by a D-ring, chin details on both sides based on the front center line, cigarette pants with a shape that narrows to the hem, a central crease line, and a neat finish with back darts.

name: Side slit fitted pants
description: Features soft-touch, stretchy slack fabric, front center console zipper opening, front side seam hidden pockets, back center waist slit detail, fitted silhouette with a slightly widening line at the hem, deep slits on both sides of the hem, and both sides of the back. Dart and welt pockets.

name: Triple tuck volume pants
description: Fabric that falls softly with a light feel, triple tuck centered around the front, no waist band, preserving the shape of the tuck, finishing the opening with two buttons and a zipper, elastic inserted into the back waist band, a silhouette that maintains the volume of the upper part of the pants at the hem.

name: Linen waist gathered trousers
description: Linen fabric with a natural texture, a high elastic band inserted into the waist band and gathered to bring out the ruffle detail, two front buttons and a zipper opening, a straight silhouette with a 9-quarter length, and pentagonal patch pockets.

name: Wide belted pants
description: It is made of soft, stretchy fabric, features a wide belt and button opening, double tuck details on both sides of the center front, diagonal side pockets featuring a fly at the opening, and is finished with a single dart at the back.

name: Elastic band straight pants
description: Light and elastic fabric, semi-relaxed silhouette with straight lines, elastic band on the back waistband for a comfortable fit.

name: Wrap style knot dress
description: Made of soft and light fabric, wrap style dress with a V-neckline, knot detail on the front, and a waistband that can be tied in the back.

name: Single button blazer wrap dress
description: Solid and heavy formal fabric, single blazer collar overlaps and fastened with buttons, front and back princess line darts emphasize waist line, fitted long sleeve dress with set-in sleeves.

name: Satin overlap jumpsuit
description: Glossy and light satin fabric, V-neck overlap style, neck fastening with inner snap, elastic band inserted into the waist cut for a relaxed fit, shirring details to create a feminine silhouette, short-length shorts, and a variety of waist straps. Long sleeves that can be styled with ample width.

name: Chelsea collar mini dress
description: Elastic black fabric, featuring a deep single-collar neck shape, button-down opening with point buttons, and darts and shirring inserted into the empire cut to create volume. Short sleeves, back yoke cut pleats, Illastek band inserted into the back waist cut and connected with yoke line shirring. A short-length mini dress.

name: Overfit unbalanced flowy dress
description: It features a light fabric with a melange collar, a deep crew neck style, generous shoulder width with dropped shoulders, front open patch pockets, an unbalanced shape with different lengths on the front and back, and the side cut lines are forwarded to the front. A boxy dress with flowing lines in an A-line silhouette.

name: Henry neck shirring dress
description: The fabric has a papery texture with a smooth surface, features a V-neck shape, a button-down opening to the high waist cut, 3/4 sleeves and a sleeve band finish, and plenty of shirring at the waist cut to create a relaxed A-line skirt silhouette. Neck, sleeve cuffs and inner hem match to give a point.

name: Princess line shirt dress
description: Single collar and button-down style shirt dress, featuring a princess line extending from the shoulder cut to the hem, cap sleeves with short sleeve length, size adjustable using waist strap, neat finish with 1/4" stitching at the end of the sleeve, woody look one button match adds specialness.

name: Short sleeve shirt dress
description: Cool, soft, wrinkle-free fabric, single-collar button-down style shirt dress, short sleeves, straight lines for a minimalist silhouette, and short-length mini dress.

name: Loose long sleeve shirt dress
description: Soft fabric featuring a wavy texture, single-collar button-down style shirt dress, generous drop shoulders, long sleeves and regular cuffs, back yoke and center back box pleats, and shirt tail shape at the bottom.

name: V-neck collar jumpsuit
description: V-neck with single collar, zipper opening below the back collar slit, generous chest width with dropped shoulders, long short sleeves and folded cuffs, size adjustable with waist strap, front and back center cut, welts on both sides of the back. Features a straight, boxy silhouette with pockets.

name: Maxi dress 047
description: Maxi dress with waist/back strings and side slits.

name: Black dress 048
description: Loose-fitting shirt dress. It features a collared neckline, button-down front, long sleeves with cuffs, and gathers at the waist that give it a flared look towards the hem. The dress has a minimalist design and an A-line silhouette. The model wearing the dress is paired with simple black sandals, and the background is plain white, emphasizing focus on the dress.

name: Henley neck sheer shirt
description: A sheer fabric with outstanding texture, a henley neck style blouse. Features a shoulder yoke and shirring. Straight silhouette, neat cuff finish.

name: Crew neck shirring shirt
description: Soft fabric with a formal mood, clean crew neck line, shoulder line crossing the front as a point, appropriate length for a variety of looks, and shirring on the top and bottom of the sleeves for a sense of volume.

name: High neck keyhole blouse
description: The drapery fabric makes the shirring detail stand out, the high neck is at an appropriate height, and the keyhole opening adds a sense of relaxation to the neck area. Comfortable fit with a moderately dropped shoulder silhouette.

name: V-neck raglan blouse
description: Henley V-neck style blouse, neatly finished with 1/4" neck binding, fabric added to the raglan sleeve cutout to add a casual mood, fabric texture that hugs the body for a comfortable fit. Buttons can be attached to the cuffs for a variety of looks.

name: Henry U-neck Blouse
description: Blouse featuring a henley neck and U-shaped neck drop, pleated details on the neck cut line add richness, high-vis fabric creates a powerful silhouette, cut in the middle of the sleeve and topstitch details, and high cuffs and inner buttons. Neat finish.

name: Double button puff
description: Fabric with outstanding texture, featuring a wide collar and double buttons, puff sleeves with deep pleats, the shirring at the end of the sleeves is held in place by a fabric band to create a rich silhouette, and a straight silhouette with a relaxed feel.

name: Crinkled roll-up shirt
description: Light fabric with a crinkled texture, slightly forward shoulder line, patch pocket detail on the left chest, space between buttons at the bottom of the body allows for a variety of looks, sleeve roll-up using buttons and straps, and pleats at the back yoke for a relaxed fit. Comfortable fit.

name: Papery hidden placket shirt
description: Papery fabric adds strength to the silhouette, features a wide hidden placket, 1/2" length short sleeve shirt, deep box pleats at the back yoke cutout, and a straight silhouette with set-in sleeves.

name: Half hidden placket shirt
description: A courtney-like fabric with a light texture, a half-length hidden button down shirt, pleats in the cutout area below the shirt opening placket, and high cuffs for a solid finish with double-layer sewing on the cuffs.

name: Triple stripe shirt
description: A neat mood with soft triple striped fabric, a dropped shoulder line running down the shoulder line, a basic button-down shirt, shirttail hem silhouette, and tone-on-tone matching of buttons and fabric.

name: Ribbon tie hidden placket shirt
description: A long collar strap creates a ribbon tie, a button-down shirt with a hidden placket, long sleeves and cuffs of an appropriate height, and a straight silhouette with set-in sleeves.

name: Ruffle neck button down shirt
description: Relatively strong fabric with few wrinkles, ruffle stand collar, neat finish with 1/4" inbinding on the inside of the neck, puff sleeves with shirring at the top and bottom of the sleeves, shoulder line, back yoke cut line, and two lines at 1/4" intervals on the armhole line. stitch detail

name: Collar ruffle shirt
description: Light fabric with a crinkled texture, slightly see-through, ruffle trim on the edge of the collar as a point, abundant shirring on the drop shoulder cutout, ruffle details added to the cuffs by holding the shirring with an elastic band, and a straight silhouette for a relaxed fit.

name: Overfit button down shirt
description: Thin fabric with a dry texture, a boxy style with a long length and an overfit, a petite-sized single collar, and the generous width of the sleeves held at the cuffs to create a voluminous silhouette.

name: Linen overfit shirt
description: Features dry textured linen fabric, round collar, topstitching at 1/4" intervals, side slits on both sides of the body hem, slits at the end of the sleeves, and three button details. The round, boxy silhouette provides a relaxed fit.

name: Overfit striped short sleeve
description: Features a soft fabric with a dry texture, a wide collar, a boxy silhouette with a relaxed fit, and a striped pattern that creates a neat mood.

name: Cotton Crossover Bubble Shirt
description: Features a soft cotton fabric with a dry texture, a wide collar, a boxy silhouette with a relaxed fit, and a striped pattern that creates a neat mood.

name: Linen short sleeve shirt
description: Features a soft linen fabric with a dry texture, a wide collar, a boxy silhouette with a relaxed fit, and a striped pattern that creates a neat mood.

name: Blue linen resort shirt
description: Features a soft linen fabric with a dry texture, a wide collar, a boxy silhouette with a relaxed fit, and a striped pattern that creates a neat mood.

name: Versatile Long Sleeve Shirt
description: Features a soft linen fabric with a dry texture, a wide collar, a boxy silhouette with a relaxed fit, and a striped pattern that creates a neat mood.

name: Side slit long skirt
description: Stretchy fabric with a firm feel, a clean-cut waistline without a waistband cut, deep darts on the front and back princess lines, a center back console zipper opening, a deep slit on the left side seam, and a midi length.
